@MyFirstWebApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5254

### Get all TodoItems
GET {{MyFirstWebApi_HostAddress}}/api/todoitem
Accept: application/json

### Get a TodoItem by ID
GET {{MyFirstWebApi_HostAddress}}/api/todoitem/1
Accept: application/json

### Create a new TodoItem
POST {{MyFirstWebApi_HostAddress}}/api/todoitem
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Learn .NET 9",
  "isCompleted": false
}

### Create another TodoItem
POST {{MyFirstWebApi_HostAddress}}/api/todoitem
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Prepare Web API exercise",
  "isCompleted": false
}

### Update an existing TodoItem
PUT {{MyFirstWebApi_HostAddress}}/api/todoitem/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "Learn ASP.NET Core 9",
  "isCompleted": true
}

### Delete a TodoItem
DELETE {{MyFirstWebApi_HostAddress}}/api/todoitem/2

### Try to get a non-existing TodoItem
GET {{MyFirstWebApi_HostAddress}}/api/todoitem/999
Accept: application/json
